sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant W as Browser<br/>(verify.fivucsas.com)
    participant API as Identity Core API<br/>(api.fivucsas.com)
    participant BIO as Biometric Service<br/>(internal-only)

    note over U,W: FACE step inside a multi-step login<br/>(hosted login / embedded widget)

    U->>W: look at the camera
    W->>W: getUserMedia capture --<br/>MediaPipe FaceLandmarker (478 pts)
    note right of W: client pre-gate (advisory only --<br/>server re-decides): face present,<br/>passive-liveness 0.45,<br/>crop to 224 x 224 JPEG

    W->>API: POST /api/v1/auth/mfa/step<br/>{sessionToken, method: FACE,<br/>image (base64)}
    API->>API: gates: MFA session valid + not consumed,<br/>account lockout guard (HTTP 423<br/>after 5 failures), rate limit

    API->>BIO: POST /api/v1/verify<br/>multipart image, X-API-Key,<br/>Docker network only
    BIO->>BIO: image validation:<br/>content type + magic bytes

    BIO->>BIO: passive liveness -- MiniFASNet<br/>(LIVENESS_MODE=passive,<br/>BACKEND=uniface)

    alt not live, or score below 0.4 floor
        BIO-->>API: 400 LIVENESS_FAILED {score}
        API->>API: MFA step FAILED (audited,<br/>counts toward lockout)
        API-->>W: step failed
        W-->>U: try again -- live camera required
    else liveness passed
        note over BIO: continues in part (b):<br/>detect, quality, embed, match, veto
    end
